@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Solicitar Magic Link
# @name magicLink
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/magic-link
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teste@exemplo.com"
}

### 2. Verificar token (copie o token da resposta acima)
# @name verify
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{magicLink.response.body.magicLink}}"
}

